# Scraper Service

Entry: [scrapers/AGENTS.md](../../scrapers/AGENTS.md) -> [scrapers/.agent/index.md](../../scrapers/.agent/index.md).

## Stack

FastAPI, Playwright, Celery, PostgreSQL, Redis (DB 0 queue, DB 1 cache).

## Conventions

- Active sites: `gm`, `ml`, `vw`, `eu`, `pecadireta`; `melibox` optional.
- Router always sends `force_refresh: false` — cache lives in worker (24h TTL).
- New scrapers extend `BaseScraper` in `src/scrapers/base.py`.
- Run `make -C scrapers test lint` before marking work done.

## Out of scope

StokAPI routes, Redis Streams worker, `cdp_stokapi.json` receiver logic.
